\begin{array}{ccc}
  T_{abc}  & = & (D\Gamma_a)_{bc} + {1 \over 2}( \Omega_{abc} - \Omega_{acb})  \\

  T_{{\dot 5}ab} & = & (D\Gamma_{\dot 5})_{ab} + {1 \over 2}(\Omega_{{\dot 5}ab} - \Omega_{{\dot 5}ba}) \\
